lead_paragraph: Asian soccer said it was looking forward to working with new FIFA President Gianni Infantino, despite the region's two candidates losing out to the Swiss in Friday's election, and called for unity to help push the reform process forward.

headline.print_headline: Asia Calls for Unity to Drive FIFA Reform After Infantino Win
